## Limitations

The information gathered is based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of wireless communication security. The rapidly evolving nature of technology means that new risks and safeguards may emerge that are not covered in this report. Additionally, the effectiveness of safeguards can vary based on the specific configuration and usage of wireless networks.